Post-Match Reflections: Will Hardy said he wasn't happy with Keyonte George's defense in the first half, but still gave him 34 total minutes, collecting 9 points on 4/12 shooting, 5 rebounds, and 3 assists.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Keyonte George was benched at the start of the second half, with Isaiah Collier filling in at the one, and finishing the game with a career-high 26 minutes, posting 4 points, 8 assists, and 2 steals.
Others: The Utah Jazz lost to the Los Angeles Clippers, 105-116, dropping to their 10th loss of the year, and ending their two-game losing streak.
